commitResults.messageBody:
Renamed chatbot from Duke to Donezo. Replaced all traces of Duke with
Donezo

commitResults.messageTitle: feat: add echo and exit functionality to chatbot
feat: add list and basic storage functionality to chatbot
commitResults.messageBody:
Add the ability to store user input and display them back to the user
when requested

commitResults.messageTitle: feat: Add ability to mark task as complete and incomplete
feat: add support for tracking 3 new types of tasks
commitResults.messageBody:
Added support for the Chatbot to track ToDos, Events and Deadlines
tasks.

Fixed bug where Deadline Task will be created with 'deadline' as its
description instead of the actual description of the task

commitResults.messageTitle: feat: add error handling for the 3 types of task
commitResults.messageBody:
Added proper handling to deal with incorrect inputs from the users of
the chatbot

commitResults.messageTitle: feat: add support for deleting tasks from list
commitResults.messageBody:
Refactored the logic so that the delete functionality is in the same
method as the other commands, for easier error handling

commitResults.messageTitle: test: added test for main functionality of chatbot
commitResults.messageBody: Testing the list, event, todo, deadline, delete commands functionality

commitResults.messageTitle: test: add test support for mark/unmark commands
